            <title>[LU-14801] Improve the performance of &quot;lfs find -perm&quot; by checking on the MDT</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14801</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The current implementation of the &quot;-perm&quot; predicate for &quot;lfs find&quot; asks the OST for the permissions of the file. This is not necessary as this information is already available on the MDT.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
